Nape ihji Eesusia ahpo weerewakamera, seenepi waꞌapi ooweparepua Riosiwichio, tatakoritiameo ahsieme choꞌwemichio. Waꞌa iintosaapa puuua, ahpo Noonomina ahjamina yasiparepua, teꞌta iyoriwa yasirachiopua, ahpo Noono yawichituwa apoepechi yawichitumia.
