Pukaepa Eesusia iꞌka weeechi oiyaiopua, Riosi kaꞌkaruma tuuyewari tuuyerepua, yooma aaata tatakorichi wahjipakameka teꞌteriameo, ahpo Noonochi eꞌenamichiopua, puꞌka ki kaawe noonowiriao, cheriwepuawichioopua, ahpo weemera ahjari kiapuawichioopua tiame, Riosi Riosiwarichi teꞌtereka mochitomichiopua, iꞌka wehjoarichi mochikaiopua pehjio.
