Iꞌka ehkoriami Riosi naꞌnayewatura chaachapariao, aaataai ki sewina tiiame chaachapametepua ahpo masitiachio, aapoeche waꞌapi machename kaawe chaachapaniameo. Aapoe ehkoriami Riosi naꞌnayewaturaai, ki aapoe ahpo inatarichi eꞌra chaachapatiame puuua,
Nape iꞌka weee kajuyachio Riosia, teꞌta ahpo utewarieo, chaachasache tajenatemeripua yomatiame iꞌka weeeo, ahkasi tewekaopua tiame. Waꞌa iintomeri Riosia, teꞌta ahpo katewiachi taawechiopua, yooma nanaarame katewesa kokosaiopua.
Nape waꞌa tiiaipua, Riosie Weratiameo ahsieme eꞌwewa iintoriopa, yomatiame Riosi nuurari eꞌwepakaopua iꞌwa weeechi oirioio, weemera tiiame Riosi nuurari eꞌwewa, enepakamepua. Ehpeo eemeai Riosieo, yomatiame ahpo Taana Eesusichi paparameo, ahsepari eꞌwekame taamo tetewamepua ahpo nuurario. Pukaepa ehkoriami tukapari Riosi nuurarichi nokisitiamea, puuua saipatoamepua, ehpeo taamoo Riosi Taanara tahjewarachi mochitoamekopa, Eesusichi paparakao. Ehpeo eemea Eesusi tahjewarachi mochitoamea, kaawe ahpo nakika mochitoamepua.
Aaata teꞌta Riosie Weratiamechi kaawe teeretoamea, kiisi oiyamepua tatakoriwachio; tatakoriwachi oika puꞌseriamea, kihta Riosie Weratiamechi teeretoamepua, puuua Riosie Weratiameo, kiisi machiyameka teeretoka yasitoamepua.
Riosia seenepioi, ki aaatae tetewiniamepua; nape ahpo kaawe nakika mochitoniachi, tetewiniamepua pukachio, teꞌta kaaweruma Riosichi eename nakiwariaa, puuu Riosi nakirewaa, kaawe ahpo nakika mochitoamerakachi, epeche epecheche tamochi teetopasiamepua.
